title: Elegant Midrise, Island Kitchens, Walking distance to Fine Dining
posting_body: With condo quality finishes and all tile flooring, this new elegant luxury mid-rise in the heart of North Dallas makes the perfect home.
Entertain in your new luxury apartment.

From a night out on the town to a relaxing evening at home in your luxury apartment, This Apartments offer the best of both worlds.
